This thread summarises just some of what was achieved during 2021, along with our weekly community focussed AMAs 👑

We would like to thank each and every holder, along with our amazing community managers and vampire enforcers.

We can't wait to show you what 2022 will bring 🩸

We announced our partnership with #ScreamMovie on the 17th December in the first-ever NFT x Major Film Franchise Collab. This collaboration continues into 2022 with prizes for SVS Vampire Holders prior to the #Scream5 Release on January 14th 😱

https://t.co/1oEQL4fkA8 https://t.co/hmBYX3YgQ9

Our 12 Days of Holidays Giveaways began on December 13th, just before announcing our partnership with MintPS by Paradigm Sports.

Our collaboration with @JakePaul and @BoxingBullies also began on 16th December, raising money via Charity Auctions together 🥊

On the 8th December, we announced our plans to include a Cross-Chain Ghost Bridge, to continue building without excessive gas execution costs.

We also deployed a Polygon Contract to Airdrop Polygon Ghost Copies to SVS Holders currently staking for $BLOOD

https://t.co/7udXgCwZ7O https://t.co/oLnNgCFlav

During November, we also hosted a Vampire Meme Contest, Lore Contest and launched SVS Alpha: with exclusive access to the most hyped upcoming projects🩸

https://t.co/Nt9oQ15MAu

We also announced the Beta Launch for our official SVS Platform Game 🎮

https://t.co/pqdgPHyELU https://t.co/47qQ9Uqd0d

On 1st November our collaboration with #888InnerCircle began. Bringing 8 Tier's of collaborative NFTs claimable over the following 7 Days, with prizes for reaching specific tiers! 😇

https://t.co/mIXvdi6VVf

We also welcomed @BrianDEvans as a Project Advisor on 2nd November! 💪 https://t.co/2dFqh4DYAp

By the 16th October, both our Netherlands & NYC Billboards were live, bringing the Vamps worldwide!

Leading up to Halloween, we launched our Halloween Art Contest, our Bat Companion Claim opened (Just pay Gas!), and we partnered with @WilderWorld: sending the Vamps to Wiami! 🏎️ https://t.co/R799lkDwHY

On the 10th October we provided a sneak peak of the Bat Companions 🦇

We also partnered with Shammi Shinh, creator of Goût de Diamants: The worlds most expensive champagne. SVS Holders will be able to receive a private label, exclusive champagne shortly in 2022, via $BLOOD 🍾

On the 8th October we announced the introduction of out $BLOOD Utility Token, which launched a week later on 15th October 🩸

https://t.co/l0Mcu6oLs5

Within 24 hours, 25% of Vampires were already staked. We also announced our official partnership with @TheSandboxGame! 👌 https://t.co/AKxo2LlEz6

The 22nd September marked our Free Merchandise Claim. Every holder was able to claim a free piece of merch from our store!

On the 6th October, we met with @sandstormmeetup in @TheSandboxGame, which was followed by the launch of our Bats Derivatives contest the next day 🦇

On the 18th September, we held our first derivatives contest for the Christie's NFT Auction. We also launched our 'Syndicate Directory', allowing for browsing, and downloading of HD Vamps 🧛

We also donated 45 ETH on 20th September, to AFSP, Cancer Org & Forgotten Animals 🐶

On the 9th and 12th September we held our pre-sale and public sale, which was a great success with no gas war!

https://t.co/aGbPWSPKXU 💨

The reveal occurred the following day on 13th September, in which we had a 50% Holder Rate across the collection of 8,888. https://t.co/E5Cg3nGFzI
